HOW TO INSTALL:
----------------------

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install python3 python3-pip python3-venv git
git clone https://github.com/fixploit03/deathpy.git
cd deathpy
python3 -m venv .modules
source .modules/bin/activate
pip3 install -r requirements.txt

RUN:
----------------------
cd src
sudo python3 --help

- ^_^ -
